abstract: The teams combined for 67 points in Week 10, and Las Vegas set the over/under for this matchup at 52.5.
lead_paragraph: Don’t let Tennessee’s focus on the run fool you: All indications ahead of this game are that it could easily turn into a high-scoring affair. Las Vegas set the over/under for the game at 52.5 — six points higher than the prediction for the N.F.C. championship game — and considering that the teams combined for 67 points in Week 10, that number could easily push higher.
